The sense of jitters

00:01:26.152 --> 00:01:27.921
among the Israeli public here

00:01:27.921 --> 00:01:29.089
among the leadership

00:01:29.089 --> 00:01:29.789
in Israel

00:01:29.789 --> 00:01:31.257
about precisely what they'll do,

00:01:31.257 --> 00:01:33.226
and it's unclear what they'll do.

00:01:33.226 --> 00:01:34.294
Will they respond

00:01:34.294 --> 00:01:36.129
in straight back directly

00:01:36.129 --> 00:01:38.364
to Israel themselves with the use proxies

00:01:38.431 --> 00:01:39.666
to strike into Israel

00:01:39.666 --> 00:01:40.633
with a strike,

00:01:40.633 --> 00:01:41.734
Israeli interests

00:01:41.734 --> 00:01:43.403
elsewhere in the region?

