the IDF spokesperson, just last night,

00:02:15.368 --> 00:02:18.238
speaking about how prepared Israeli

00:02:18.271 --> 00:02:20.573
is for whatever threat comes from Iran.

00:02:22.275 --> 00:02:23.910
