00:02:28.615 --> 00:02:30.850
We're ready in both defense and defense

00:02:30.850 --> 00:02:31.951
with the various IDF

00:02:31.951 --> 00:02:34.154
capabilities and strategic partners.

00:02:34.454 --> 00:02:34.754
I'll take

00:02:34.754 --> 00:02:36.122
you should give key

00:02:36.122 --> 00:02:36.990
of Iran

00:02:36.990 --> 00:02:38.925
a strike coming from Iranian territory

00:02:38.925 --> 00:02:39.859
will clearly prove

00:02:39.859 --> 00:02:41.127
that Iranian intentions

00:02:41.127 --> 00:02:42.495
to escalate the situation

00:02:42.495 --> 00:02:43.596
in the Middle East

00:02:43.596 --> 00:02:45.632
and to stop hiding behind its proxies

00:02:48.735 --> 00:02:50.003
And I think you get

00:02:50.003 --> 00:02:51.571
a level of the understanding

00:02:51.571 --> 00:02:53.540
of how this concern is shared

00:02:53.540 --> 00:02:55.141
jointly between the United States

00:02:55.141 --> 00:02:57.177
and Israel State Department

