what Iran's move is going to be.

00:03:10.456 --> 00:03:12.825
The sense that it could be soon, Wolf.

00:03:12.825 --> 00:03:13.059
You know,

00:03:13.059 --> 00:03:14.027
there's a lot of concern

00:03:14.027 --> 00:03:15.895
in those embassy, the US embassy

00:03:15.895 --> 00:03:17.830
and other embassies in Israel as well

00:03:17.830 --> 00:03:19.966
are issuing warnings to their citizens

00:03:19.966 --> 00:03:20.700
to stay put

00:03:20.700 --> 00:03:21.701
basically

00:03:21.701 --> 00:03:22.335
and worry

00:03:22.335 --> 00:03:24.370
or start worrying about the potential.

